title: Bug 121682: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when trying to export data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export data from the report, an exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
EB: Exporting the data in the table should not result in an exception. The data should be successfully exported.
SR:
To reproduce:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Attempt to export the data in the table.
